	\'95	Plans are similarly dynamic. They are rarely complete or linear but instead take shape through the iterative process of accumulation, reflection, and action.\
	\'95	Seeing the pile as the plan requires acknowledging its 
\f0\b living potential
\f1\b0 :\
\pard\pardeftab720\li1060\fi-1060\partightenfactor0
\cf2 	\'95	Each piece in the pile represents a step, an idea, or a possibility.\
	\'95	The pile\'92s chaos holds the raw materials for structure and progress.\
\pard\pardeftab720\li520\fi-520\partightenfactor0
